description:
This “Touhou Collaborations Pack” contains collaborations between popular Touhou acts!
Enjoy the musical mixes that they've created!
And the new artist this time is Astral Sky, in a collaboration with Morimori Atsushi!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・Shuki☆RaiRai!!! / ShinRa-Bansho x COOL&CREATE
・【TOUHOU nicokara】Secret God Matara feat.TamaOnSen【IOSYS】 / IOSYS
・Eien ni Tsuzuku Yume / BUTAOTOME feat. TamaOnSen
・ReverFace / TUMENECO & GET IN THE RING
・Shooting Star feat. Risa Yuzuki / uma vs. Morimori Atsushi (Astral Sky vs. non-retrogradable rhythm)
・Sensyaku Zeshou No Fantasia / Hakurei Jinja Reitaisai Collabo Unit

■Six challenge stages total
・Lv. 5: Hum It? No, Sing It! (Sensyaku Zeshou No Fantasia)
・Lv. 6: An Unwelcome Guest (Shuki☆RaiRai!!!)
・Lv. 7: A Neverending...Nightmare?! (Eien ni Tsuzuku Yume)
・Lv. 8: Frank to a Fault! (【TOUHOU nicokara】Secret God Matara feat.TamaOnSen【IOSYS】)
・Lv. 9: Poker Face (ReverFace)
・Lv. 10: By the Light of the Stars (Shooting Star feat. Risa Yuzuki)

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Collaborations Pack
